{
  "title": "Intensely Mustardy Thai Pak Choi Curry",
  "description": "A Jain-friendly Thai dish featuring pak choi, bonito shave, and a blend of mustardy flavors, served in a terracotta dish. This meal prep curry is crumbly and full of flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Thai",
